[2]
From: brnbaum@unixg.ubc.ca (David Birnbaum)
In addition to standard texts, you might try Paryani SG et al., Intrauterine
Infection with Varicella-Zoster Virus after Maternal Varicella, N ENGL J MED
1986;314(24):1542-6, and the subsequent letter by by Preblud SR et al., N
ENGL J MED 1986;315(22):1416-7. These references, located by searching the
PARADIGM database, summarize a prospective case series and meta-analysis.
--
David Birnbaum, PhD, MPH
Clinical Assistant Professor
Dept. of Health Care & Epidemiology
University of British Columbia
e-mail: brnbaum@unixg.ubc.ca
